      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a budget-friendly way to get on the road? This car is in poor condition and will need some dedicated TLC to get back to its best, but it offers a fantastic foundation for someone who loves a hands-on challenge! It\u2019s an honest vehicle with plenty of character, perfect for a mechanic's special or a restoration enthusiast ready to bring it back to life.",
