      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, it\u2019s like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or smudge anywhere! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it still has that fresh, new-car feel. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for perfection, this is it! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
