      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional 1995 Mazda RX-7 FD, preserved in a state of mechanical and aesthetic excellence. This specimen features the legendary 13B-REW rotary engine, exhibiting optimal compression across all rotor faces. The sequential twin-turbocharged induction system remains unmodified, providing a seamless transition between primary and secondary boost phases. The longitudinal front-midship chassis maintains its factory double-wishbone suspension geometry, paired with a Torsen limited-slip differential for precise power distribution. The 5-speed manual transaxle offers tight, positive shifts, and the cooling system has been meticulously serviced to prevent thermal soak. With pristine original paint and an interior free of UV degradation, this is an investment-grade example of the pinnacle of Japanese performance engineering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
